name: Charles Fahselt
body:
### Welcome to Charles' Page.
Hello, my name is Charles Fahselt, and I am a recent graduate from UHCL with a Bachelors in Computer Science. Here is my Github page, where I plan to showcase all of my projects and hobbies.

### Interests
I love coding, especially in Java, but I am also familiar with many languages, including:
* HTML, CSS, Javascript, ASP.NET and C#
* C++, x86 Assembly


### Projects
I have dabbled with many projects, but I have only polished a few well enough to be uploaded onto my GitHub.
* [Drone Control](https://github.com/fahseltc/Drone-Control). For my senior project at UHCL, I worked on a team to develop a Quad-copter Simulator and Controller.
* [Pac-Dan](https://github.com/fahseltc/Pac-Dan). In my free time, I worked on a Pac-Man clone using LibGDX
* [Neural Networks](https://github.com/fahseltc/NeuralNetwork). I have also worked on a project involving Neural Networks, which I find to be a very interesting topic.
